to the invisible magnetic field.

00:20:39.730 --> 00:20:43.920 align:middle line:84%
Eistein-- the field is
the sole governing agency

00:20:43.920 --> 00:20:46.520 align:middle line:84%
of the particle-- in this
case, the iron filings.

00:20:46.520 --> 00:20:49.320 align:middle line:84%
And the relevance
about this is matter

00:20:49.320 --> 00:20:52.920 align:middle line:90%
plus field equals structure.

00:20:52.920 --> 00:20:54.360 align:middle line:90%
Matter without field?

00:20:54.360 --> 00:20:56.550 align:middle line:90%
Random pile.

00:20:56.550 --> 00:21:01.320 align:middle line:84%
And all of a sudden it says then
the structure that you express

00:21:01.320 --> 00:21:03.330 align:middle line:84%
is not due to just
the structure.

00:21:03.330 --> 00:21:06.630 align:middle line:84%
It's due to the fields
around this structure.

00:21:06.630 --> 00:21:09.330 align:middle line:84%
Now, let's look at that
slide of iron filings

00:21:09.330 --> 00:21:10.470 align:middle line:90%
over the magnetic field.

00:21:10.470 --> 00:21:12.510 align:middle line:84%
And now, instead
of iron filings,

00:21:12.510 --> 00:21:15.030 align:middle line:84%
let's suggest that
this is a tumor.

00:21:15.030 --> 00:21:18.083 align:middle line:84%
And those iron filings
are tumor cells.

00:21:18.083 --> 00:21:19.500 align:middle line:84%
And then I would
say, well, what's

00:21:19.500 --> 00:21:20.970 align:middle line:90%
the conventional understanding?

00:21:20.970 --> 00:21:25.440 align:middle line:84%
The allopathic Newtonian
vision is, well, this tumor

00:21:25.440 --> 00:21:27.570 align:middle line:84%
must be shaped by
something physical.

00:21:27.570 --> 00:21:29.700 align:middle line:90%
And so we take apart the cells.

00:21:29.700 --> 00:21:30.700 align:middle line:90%
And we look for what?

00:21:30.700 --> 00:21:31.770 align:middle line:90%
Onco gene.

00:21:31.770 --> 00:21:33.060 align:middle line:90%
A cancer gene.

00:21:33.060 --> 00:21:35.370 align:middle line:90%
A gene that causes this problem.

00:21:35.370 --> 00:21:36.270 align:middle line:90%
And guess what?

00:21:36.270 --> 00:21:38.740 align:middle line:84%
You can take apart all
the cells you want.

00:21:38.740 --> 00:21:41.600 align:middle line:84%
There is no gene
that caused that.

00:21:41.600 --> 00:21:44.120 align:middle line:90%
It's a field that causes that.

00:21:44.120 --> 00:21:47.660 align:middle line:84%
The field is shaping the
cells, just as the field

00:21:47.660 --> 00:21:49.190 align:middle line:90%
shapes iron filings.

00:21:49.190 --> 00:21:51.500 align:middle line:84%
And we keep looking
inside the cell to say,

00:21:51.500 --> 00:21:54.560 align:middle line:84%
where the heck did
that cancer come from?

00:21:54.560 --> 00:21:56.270 align:middle line:90%
It does not come from genes.

00:21:56.270 --> 00:21:57.630 align:middle line:90%
Simple fact.

00:21:57.630 --> 00:22:01.100 align:middle line:84%
There is no gene
that causes cancer.

00:22:01.100 --> 00:22:04.310 align:middle line:84%
I always get concerned
when women do a test

00:22:04.310 --> 00:22:07.640 align:middle line:84%
and they find that they have
the BRCA1 cancer gene, how

00:22:07.640 --> 00:22:10.370 align:middle line:84%
that really messes with their
head based on the belief

00:22:10.370 --> 00:22:11.210 align:middle line:90%
system.

00:22:11.210 --> 00:22:13.340 align:middle line:84%
Belief system--
you got the gene.

00:22:13.340 --> 00:22:15.950 align:middle line:90%
You can expect the cancer.

00:22:15.950 --> 00:22:19.205 align:middle line:84%
Angelina Jolie, she had
a double mastectomy.

00:22:19.205 --> 00:22:20.330 align:middle line:90%
She didn't have the cancer.

00:22:20.330 --> 00:22:23.380 align:middle line:84%
She just figured, because her
mother died of breast cancer,

00:22:23.380 --> 00:22:25.250 align:middle line:84%
her grandmother died
of breast cancer,

00:22:25.250 --> 00:22:27.170 align:middle line:90%
that she's going to die as well.

00:22:27.170 --> 00:22:30.510 align:middle line:84%
So she figured, if
I have a mastectomy,

00:22:30.510 --> 00:22:32.360 align:middle line:90%
I won't have the problem.

00:22:32.360 --> 00:22:34.940 align:middle line:84%
Well, that's not true,
because the same gene also

00:22:34.940 --> 00:22:37.320 align:middle line:90%
causes uterine cancers as well.

00:22:37.320 --> 00:22:38.710 align:middle line:90%
But here's the other story.

00:22:38.710 --> 00:22:40.310 align:middle line:90%
And the story is this.

00:22:40.310 --> 00:22:44.460 align:middle line:84%
Does having the BRCA1 gene mean
you're going to get the cancer?

00:22:44.460 --> 00:22:48.470 align:middle line:90%
And the answer is absolutely no.

00:22:48.470 --> 00:22:52.790 align:middle line:84%
50% of the women with the
gene never get the cancer.

00:22:52.790 --> 00:22:54.140 align:middle line:90%
This is a very important fact.

00:22:54.140 --> 00:22:55.340 align:middle line:90%
Why?

00:22:55.340 --> 00:22:59.430 align:middle line:84%
Possession of the gene
doesn't mean cancer.

00:22:59.430 --> 00:23:03.440 align:middle line:84%
It's the lifestyle associated
with possession of that gene

00:23:03.440 --> 00:23:05.330 align:middle line:90%
that will manifest the cancer.

00:23:05.330 --> 00:23:07.160 align:middle line:84%
And that's why half
the women are not

00:23:07.160 --> 00:23:10.850 align:middle line:84%
expressing a negative or
non-supporting lifestyle.

00:23:10.850 --> 00:23:12.830 align:middle line:84%
They're expressing a
normal healthy life.

00:23:12.830 --> 00:23:16.730 align:middle line:84%
And in spite of having the
gene, they won't get the cancer.

00:23:16.730 --> 00:23:20.510 align:middle line:84%
But somebody with that gene
who is not living in harmony,

00:23:20.510 --> 00:23:24.140 align:middle line:84%
not living in the balance
of the environment,

00:23:24.140 --> 00:23:26.260 align:middle line:90%
they can get the cancer.

00:23:26.260 --> 00:23:27.930 align:middle line:90%
Point simply is this--

00:23:27.930 --> 00:23:30.560 align:middle line:84%
the gene does not
cause the cancer.

00:23:30.560 --> 00:23:32.510 align:middle line:90%
It is correlated with cancer.

00:23:32.510 --> 00:23:35.000 align:middle line:90%
The cause is the field--

00:23:35.000 --> 00:23:37.280 align:middle line:90%
how we are living our lives.

00:23:37.280 --> 00:23:40.670 align:middle line:84%
And all of a sudden, this
profoundly important point

00:23:40.670 --> 00:23:43.250 align:middle line:84%
comes to the forefront
and says this.

00:23:43.250 --> 00:23:46.070 align:middle line:84%
Less than 10% of disease
has any physical connection

00:23:46.070 --> 00:23:49.890 align:middle line:84%
with our genetics and
maybe even less than 1%.

00:23:49.890 --> 00:23:55.900 align:middle line:84%
So a cancer is not a disease
as much as it is a symptom.

00:23:55.900 --> 00:23:57.890 align:middle line:90%
A cancer is a symptom.

00:23:57.890 --> 00:23:59.420 align:middle line:90%
I'm not living in harmony.

00:23:59.420 --> 00:24:00.920 align:middle line:90%
Look what I manifest.

00:24:00.920 --> 00:24:02.240 align:middle line:90%
Guess what?

00:24:02.240 --> 00:24:04.130 align:middle line:84%
Changing the
character of your life

00:24:04.130 --> 00:24:06.590 align:middle line:84%
is profoundly
important in changing

00:24:06.590 --> 00:24:08.720 align:middle line:90%
the character of a cancer.

00:24:08.720 --> 00:24:10.700 align:middle line:84%
Something called a
spontaneous remission

00:24:10.700 --> 00:24:12.290 align:middle line:90%
occurs quite frequently.

00:24:12.290 --> 00:24:14.270 align:middle line:90%
What is a spontaneous remission?

00:24:14.270 --> 00:24:16.160 align:middle line:84%
An individual is
given a prognosis

00:24:16.160 --> 00:24:18.340 align:middle line:84%
that, oh, my
goodness, you're going

00:24:18.340 --> 00:24:20.090 align:middle line:90%
to die in about three months.

00:24:20.090 --> 00:24:21.980 align:middle line:84%
I say, well, what does
that individual do?

00:24:21.980 --> 00:24:25.010 align:middle line:84%
If they buy the belief of
the doctor, guess what?

00:24:25.010 --> 00:24:27.410 align:middle line:84%
They're going to create
a consciousness that

00:24:27.410 --> 00:24:29.780 align:middle line:84%
will manifest that
physical experience.

00:24:29.780 --> 00:24:33.460 align:middle line:84%
And the cancer will kill
them in about three months.

00:24:33.460 --> 00:24:36.050 align:middle line:84%
But in contrast, other
people will go, well, wait.

00:24:36.050 --> 00:24:37.550 align:middle line:84%
If I'm going to die
in three months,

00:24:37.550 --> 00:24:40.120 align:middle line:84%
then I'm going to
quit the stupid job.

00:24:40.120 --> 00:24:42.640 align:middle line:84%
And I'm going to leave the
aggravating environment

00:24:42.640 --> 00:24:43.440 align:middle line:90%
that I'm in.

00:24:43.440 --> 00:24:44.940 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to go on
the road, and I'm

00:24:44.940 --> 00:24:47.290 align:middle line:84%
going to enjoy myself for
the last three months.

00:24:47.290 --> 00:24:48.260 align:middle line:90%
And guess what?

00:24:48.260 --> 00:24:50.110 align:middle line:90%
Three months come and go.

00:24:50.110 --> 00:24:54.400 align:middle line:84%
Six months, a year, five
years, they're still here.

00:24:54.400 --> 00:24:56.590 align:middle line:84%
What did they do
that was different?

00:24:56.590 --> 00:24:59.080 align:middle line:84%
They didn't change
the physical cancer.

00:24:59.080 --> 00:25:03.120 align:middle line:84%
They changed the environment
that promoted the cancer.

00:25:03.120 --> 00:25:06.820 align:middle line:84%
A spontaneous remission, there's
a change in the belief system,

00:25:06.820 --> 00:25:08.805 align:middle line:90%
a change in the consciousness.

00:25:08.805 --> 00:25:10.180 align:middle line:84%
And this is
profoundly important,

00:25:10.180 --> 00:25:14.200 align:middle line:84%
because this is where we have to
understand the control of life

00:25:14.200 --> 00:25:15.160 align:middle line:90%
comes from.

00:25:15.160 --> 00:25:18.370 align:middle line:90%
What is your consciousness?

00:25:18.370 --> 00:25:22.000 align:middle line:84%
Are you visioning a
healthy, happy life?

00:25:22.000 --> 00:25:24.040 align:middle line:84%
Or are you concerned that
running in your family

00:25:24.040 --> 00:25:28.420 align:middle line:84%
is cardiovascular
disease or diabetes?

00:25:28.420 --> 00:25:30.740 align:middle line:90%
Point is very simple.

00:25:30.740 --> 00:25:33.640 align:middle line:84%
What image you hold
in your consciousness

00:25:33.640 --> 00:25:37.570 align:middle line:84%
is translated into a
physical expression.

00:25:37.570 --> 00:25:40.690 align:middle line:84%
You can absolutely
change your life

00:25:40.690 --> 00:25:44.170 align:middle line:84%
by changing your consciousness,
because this is the foundation

00:25:44.170 --> 00:25:46.030 align:middle line:90%
behind epigenetics.

00:25:46.030 --> 00:25:50.050 align:middle line:84%
And this is the story of
how vibration will also

00:25:50.050 --> 00:25:52.690 align:middle line:84%
select our genes
and the character

00:25:52.690 --> 00:25:56.380 align:middle line:90%
of that genetic expression.

00:25:56.380 --> 00:25:58.520 align:middle line:84%
The insights offered
by quantum physics

00:25:58.520 --> 00:26:01.970 align:middle line:84%
really reveal the whole story
about how our consciousness is

00:26:01.970 --> 00:26:05.420 align:middle line:90%
creating our life experiences.

00:26:05.420 --> 00:26:08.930 align:middle line:84%
If I go back to 1930, just
after quantum physics came

00:26:08.930 --> 00:26:10.700 align:middle line:84%
into the world of
science, I want

00:26:10.700 --> 00:26:13.910 align:middle line:84%
to leave you with a quote
from Sir James Jeans.

00:26:13.910 --> 00:26:16.070 align:middle line:84%
"The stream of
knowledge is heading

00:26:16.070 --> 00:26:19.370 align:middle line:84%
towards a
non-mechanical reality.

00:26:19.370 --> 00:26:22.790 align:middle line:84%
The universe begins to look
more like a great thought

00:26:22.790 --> 00:26:25.160 align:middle line:90%
than like a great machine.

00:26:25.160 --> 00:26:29.300 align:middle line:84%
Mind no longer appears to
be an accidental intruder

00:26:29.300 --> 00:26:31.190 align:middle line:90%
into the realm of matter.

00:26:31.190 --> 00:26:35.120 align:middle line:84%
We ought rather hail it as
the creator and the governor

00:26:35.120 --> 00:26:37.550 align:middle line:90%
of the realm of matter."

00:26:37.550 --> 00:26:39.950 align:middle line:84%
And to follow that
up, at the same time,

00:26:39.950 --> 00:26:42.470 align:middle line:84%
Sir Arthur Eddington,
another physicist, wrote,

00:26:42.470 --> 00:26:45.560 align:middle line:84%
"It is difficult for the
matter of fact physicists

00:26:45.560 --> 00:26:50.390 align:middle line:84%
to accept the view that the
substratum of everything

00:26:50.390 --> 00:26:53.860 align:middle line:90%
is a mental character."

00:26:53.860 --> 00:26:56.650 align:middle line:84%
These two physicists
are actually

00:26:56.650 --> 00:26:58.660 align:middle line:84%
giving us the most
important conclusions

00:26:58.660 --> 00:27:00.370 align:middle line:90%
of quantum physics--

00:27:00.370 --> 00:27:04.330 align:middle line:84%
that mind and consciousness
and energy fields

00:27:04.330 --> 00:27:07.670 align:middle line:84%
are what shape our
life experiences.

00:27:07.670 --> 00:27:09.800 align:middle line:84%
And when we understand
that, then we say, well,

00:27:09.800 --> 00:27:11.790 align:middle line:84%
