change your life, you

00:27:11.790 --> 00:27:13.900 align:middle line:84%
don't have to do
anything physical.

00:27:13.900 --> 00:27:16.120 align:middle line:84%
But you do have to do
something in regard

00:27:16.120 --> 00:27:18.770 align:middle line:90%
to your consciousness.

00:27:18.770 --> 00:27:23.050 align:middle line:84%
So in conclusion, what
does this mean for you?

00:27:23.050 --> 00:27:25.090 align:middle line:84%
The quality of
life is profoundly

00:27:25.090 --> 00:27:27.460 align:middle line:90%
influenced by energy.

00:27:27.460 --> 00:27:29.980 align:middle line:84%
When energy waves
interfere with each other,

00:27:29.980 --> 00:27:32.560 align:middle line:84%
they may express
constructive interference

00:27:32.560 --> 00:27:36.790 align:middle line:84%
