00:27:39.940 --> 00:27:42.640 align:middle line:84%
To learn how we can
control our consciousness

00:27:42.640 --> 00:27:45.130 align:middle line:84%
and manifest the
life we desire, it

00:27:45.130 --> 00:27:47.800 align:middle line:84%
is first necessary
to understand how

00:27:47.800 --> 00:27:50.920 align:middle line:84%
cells manage environmental
signals and controlling

00:27:50.920 --> 00:27:53.140 align:middle line:90%
behavior and genetics.

